WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:04.033
The Empress Dowager was poisoned by my Southern Border secret potion.

2
00:00:04.133 --> 00:00:07.566
I was originally the Holy Maiden of the Southern Border.

3
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.833
Years ago,

4
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.300
I was saved by the National Madam.

5
00:00:12.366 --> 00:00:14.300
I then stayed in Songjiang.

6
00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:19.266
I have watched the Empress Dowager grow up since she was a child.

7
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:23.966
I was the Empress Dowager’s nanny.

8
00:00:26.966 --> 00:00:27.766
Jiang Momo.

9
00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:32.366
The Empress Dowager is to confer a title to a certain Concubine tomorrow.

10
00:00:32.366 --> 00:00:34.166
This is a great event!

11
00:00:34.766 --> 00:00:36.766
Congratulations to the Concubine. Don’t be a Concubine.

12
00:00:36.933 --> 00:00:40.666
I want to be the Empress.

13
00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:44.100
Help me.

14
00:00:44.766 --> 00:00:46.066
It’s all my fault.

15
00:00:48.533 --> 00:00:52.266
All the mistakes are mine.

16
00:00:52.566 --> 00:00:55.633
It’s all my doing.

17
00:00:56.466 --> 00:00:57.300
Ah!

18
00:00:57.866 --> 00:00:59.266
Princess and the Empress Dowager,

19
00:00:59.300 --> 00:01:02.466
you are both as evil as me.

20
00:01:02.466 --> 00:01:04.266
You are both responsible.

21
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:06.700
I will spare you death

22
00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:08.166
for killing my niece.

23
00:01:08.166 --> 00:01:09.200
But you cannot escape punishment.

24
00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:11.600
From now on, you are exiled to Shu.

25
00:01:11.733 --> 00:01:13.766
You will never enter the imperial city again.

26
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:16.033
As for the others, including the Concubine,

27
00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:18.200
they will all be sent to the Supreme Court.

28
00:01:18.366 --> 00:01:19.866
Tomorrow, they will be executed.

29
00:01:21.266 --> 00:01:23.500
Take them all away.

30
00:01:24.366 --> 00:01:25.433
Your Majesty,

31
00:01:27.933 --> 00:01:29.000
Ah!

32
00:01:35.533 --> 00:01:36.466
Your Majesty,

33
00:01:37.100 --> 00:01:38.866
Master Shen has returned.

34
00:01:40.166 --> 00:01:41.466
Mother, please rest.

35
00:01:41.466 --> 00:01:43.066
I will take my leave now.

36
00:01:46.166 --> 00:01:47.233
Greetings, Your Majesty.

37
00:01:47.266 --> 00:01:49.266
Have you discovered anything, Your Majesty?

38
00:01:49.366 --> 00:01:50.633
During the investigation,

39
00:01:50.766 --> 00:01:53.200
I found that the divine physician by Prince Duan’s side and the one by Prince Rui’s side

40
00:01:53.466 --> 00:01:54.800
are the same person.

41
00:01:55.333 --> 00:01:57.833
Prince Duan is merely a decoy,

42
00:01:57.900 --> 00:02:00.100
and the real mastermind is Prince Rui.

43
00:02:00.466 --> 00:02:03.266
The divine physician managed to avoid my search

44
00:02:03.533 --> 00:02:05.866
because he has been hiding in Prince Rui’s residence,

45
00:02:06.133 --> 00:02:07.400
under Prince Rui’s protection.
